---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '../../i18n/utils';

const t = useTranslations('pt-br');
---

<Layout title={t('cv.title')} description="Curriculum vitae – Felipe Lamarca" lang="pt-BR">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <header>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-2">{t('cv.title')}</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">{t('cv.subtitle')}</p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dFBrI109flg6zSQHnFIxUd1DRfieCYAT/view?usp=sharing"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 text-sm border border-border dark:border-border-dark rounded-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark hover:border-accent dark:hover:border-accent-dark hover:text-accent dark:hover:text-accent-dark transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
          {t('cv.download')}
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Afiliações</h2>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-accent dark:border-accent-dark pl-5 space-y-1">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
            Cientista de Dados <span class="text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark font-normal">@</span>
            <a href="https://atlasintel.org/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AtlasIntel</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark leading-relaxed">
            A AtlasIntel fornece produtos de dados avançados para inteligência política e previsão econômica. Meu trabalho envolve calibração de amostras de surveys, análise política, monitoramento de opinião pública e melhoria de pipelines de dados internos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-accent dark:border-accent-dark pl-5 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Pesquisador <span class="text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark font-normal">@</span> IESP-UERJ</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                <a href="https://mape.org.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MAPE</a>
                <span class="text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark font-normal text-sm ml-1">· coordenado por Fernando Meireles &amp; Bruno Schaefer</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Laboratório de Monitoramento e Avaliação de Políticas Públicas e Eleições. Dedicado ao estudo de políticas públicas, eleições e suas interconexões por meio de técnicas de inferência causal e aprendizado de máquina.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                <a href="https://www.lab-doxa.org.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOXA</a>
                <span class="text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark font-normal text-sm ml-1">· coordenado por Fernando Meireles &amp; Argelina Cheibub Figueiredo</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Laboratório de Estudos Eleitorais, de Comunicação Política e Opinião Pública. Um dos principais centros de pesquisa sobre processos eleitorais, comunicação política e comportamento de voto no Brasil.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                <a href="http://necon.iesp.uerj.br" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NECON</a>
                <span class="text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark font-normal text-sm ml-1">· coordenado por Fabiano Santos</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Núcleo de Estudos sobre o Congresso. Focado em pesquisa acadêmica sobre o Legislativo brasileiro, incluindo bases de dados sobre votações nominais, migração partidária e produção legislativa.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">{t('cv.education')}</h2>
      <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2024–atual</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark font-medium">Mestrado em Ciência Política</p>
            <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm"><a href="https://iesp.uerj.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instituto de Estudos Sociais e Políticos</a> (IESP-UERJ)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2021–2024</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark font-medium">Bacharelado em Ciência de Dados e Inteligência Artificial</p>
            <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm"><a href="https://emap.fgv.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Escola de Matemática Aplicada</a> (FGV EMAp)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2019–2024</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark font-medium">Bacharelado em Ciências Sociais</p>
            <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark text-sm"><a href="https://cpdoc.fgv.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Escola de Ciências Sociais</a> (FGV CPDOC)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">{t('cv.scholarships')}</h2>
      <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2026–2027</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bolsa de Pesquisa de Pós-Graduação — FAPERJ Nota 10 (Fundação de Amparo à Pesquisa do Estado do Rio de Janeiro).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2025–2026</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bolsa de Pesquisa de Pós-Graduação — CAPES (Coordenação de Aperfeiçoamento de Pessoal de Nível Superior).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2021–2022</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bolsa de Iniciação Científica Institucional — CNPq.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2019–2021</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bolsa de Iniciação Científica Institucional — FGV.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2019–2024</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bolsa de Mérito de 90% para estudos de graduação na FGV, concedida por desempenho excepcional no exame de admissão.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">{t('cv.distinctions')}</h2>
      <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2026</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">2º Colocado, Best DH Tool or Suite of Tools – <a href="http://dhawards.org/dhawards2025/results/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DH Awards 2025</a>, pelo projeto <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/RelicarIA" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RelicarIA</a> (trabalho conjunto com Danielle Sanches de Almeida).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2026</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Selecionado para receber a Bolsa de Pós-Graduação FAPERJ Nota 10 por desempenho excepcional no primeiro ano do Mestrado em Ciência Política no IESP-UERJ.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2025</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Prêmio de Distinção Acadêmica Professor Carlos Eduardo Sarmento, Escola de Ciências Sociais (FGV CPDOC), pelo melhor desempenho acadêmico entre os formandos da turma de 2025.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2024</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">1º lugar no ingresso ao Mestrado em Ciência Política no IESP-UERJ.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0 sm:w-28">2020</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Melhor Trabalho, Semana de História e Ciências Sociais (FGV CPDOC).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">{t('cv.conferences')}</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark mb-4">Conferências frequentadas como participante e atividades de treinamento. Para apresentações, ver <a href="/pt-br/publications" class="link">Publicações</a>.</p>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3 border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0">Fevereiro 2026</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">
            <a href="https://www.effectivealtruism.org/ea-global" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Effective Altruism Global</a> – San Francisco, CA, Estados Unidos (financiamento integral).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3 border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0">Novembro 2025</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">
            Escrita acadêmica e publicação de artigos quantitativos em Ciências Sociais @ IESP-UERJ.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3 border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0">Julho 2025</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">
            Advanced Text-As-Data: Word Embeddings, Deep Learning, and LLMs @ IESP-UERJ.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3 border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0">Julho 2024</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">
            <a href="https://sicss.io/2024/fgv-ecmi-brazil/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SICSS: Summer Institute in Computational Social Science</a> – Rio de Janeiro, RJ, Brasil.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 py-3 border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark shrink-0">Julho 2024</span>
          <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">
            <a href="https://www.ml4good.org/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ML4Good Bootcamp</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">{t('cv.references')}</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border dark:border-border-dark">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Nome</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Instituição</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Para</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">E-mail</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Fernando Meireles, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa e Ensino</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">fernando <span>dot</span> meireles <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Jaqueline Zulini, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">FGV CPDOC</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">jaqueline <span>dot</span> zulini <span>at</span> fgv <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Bruno Schaefer, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa e Ensino</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">brunoschaefer <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Argelina Figueiredo, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">argelina <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">José Szwako, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">zeszwako <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Rogério Barbosa, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">rogerio <span>dot</span> barbosa <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Fabiano Santos, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">IESP-UERJ</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">fsantos <span>at</span> iesp <span>dot</span> uerj <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Luiz Max Carvalho, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">FGV EMAp</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">luiz <span>dot</span> fagundes <span>at</span> fgv <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Renato Rocha Souza, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">University of Vienna</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">renato <span>dot</span> rocha <span>dot</span> souza <span>at</span> univie <span>dot</span> ac <span>dot</span> at</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Jimmy Medeiros, Ph.D.</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">FGV CPDOC</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Pesquisa e Ensino</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">jimmy <span>dot</span> medeiros <span>at</span> fgv <span>dot</span> br</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
